Generate Stochastics

Source: R/stochastics.R
generate_stochastics.Rd

Generate Stochastics

generate_stochastics(months, processes = 3)

Arguments

months

An integer of the number of projection months.
processes

Defaults to three stochastic processes.

Value

An MxN matrix of stochastic random variables

Examples

generate_stochastics(3,360)
